    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AggregatedData
    Represents aggregated consumption data for a specific provider over a defined period.
    AggregatedDataRepository
    Repository interface for AggregatedData entities.
    DataAggregationService
    Service responsible for aggregating meter readings from various providers and storing the summarized data.
    DataCollectionService
    Service responsible for collecting meter readings from external providers and storing them in the database.
    MeterReading
    Represents a meter reading submitted by a specific provider.
    MeterReadingRepository
    Repository interface for MeterReading entities.
    MeterReadingRepositoryCustom
    Custom repository interface for MeterReading entities.
    MeterReadingRepositoryImpl
    Implementation of the MeterReadingRepositoryCustom interface.
    ProviderProperties
    Configuration properties for external service providers.
    ProviderProperties.ProviderConfig
    Configuration details for a single external service provider.
    SmartcitymicroserviceApplication
    The entry point for the Smart City Microservice application.
